ass=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa8179230c567a3ccefa22df4c0e2331c4e815b","tid":2357424,"uid":23058,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:04:03.000Z","msg":"鄭狗幾時死"},{"pid":"4998e4ff311c5258a57cb4657aef523a09aba03c","tid":2357424,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:07:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313a7726c0ffc69ae465ac6c3726dfefeaeda77e","tid":2357424,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6c8e5e1634c7f7a4f28da242d4e6e2d881ddd013","tid":2357424,"uid":282347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:02:39.000Z","msg":"律師並非活在象牙塔之中，當然知道社會運動的情況<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:11:16.000Z","msg":"大把好似黃國桐嘅律師幫手足, 佢地更加唔出名都係普通人點會唔知"},{"pid":"7b838ca6b1042799328c5af563c16407adc557c6","tid":2357424,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:13:30.000Z","msg":"咁尖啲箭，射出嚟唔少嘢喎<br />\n<br />\n唔係話射唔出 同有其他用途咩"},{"pid":"0b226a7ce0e89ea4076f54b0f20dfd31a1aa05c0","tid":2357424,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:14:12.000Z","msg":"鄭狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"888e6b25f5a5e6512f826b76ee1865af3bca2abf","tid":2357424,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b90c356b9422eea182804fba061aa3a7e1fdd0c","tid":2357424,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:27:09.000Z","msg":"上訴方續指，裁判官表明分開考慮被告帶出街和留在家中的弩，結果憑被告街上衣著和社會過去半年的狀況，就斷定家中的弩用於傷人，推論非常危險，尤其現場不是公眾地方，很多人家中也有可以傷人的物品。"},{"pid":"0ee57ad1b61a658d2d016ad6f0439c6eead950e6","tid":2357424,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:28:13.000Z","msg":"高院法官張慧玲指，前年爆發激烈示威，有人受傷，亦有財物受損，示威者曾用過弓箭等，這些是人所共知的事實。張官又謂，就當裁判官自行觀察元旦事態有不公，她現在重新審視證據，又可否考慮這些事實。上訴方指現在無法重新舉證，若考慮元旦當日以外的情況，恐怕更加不公。<br />\n<br />\n張官又指，被告當日一身黑色裝束，袋裡還攜有頭盔、「V煞」面具、防毒面罩、護目鏡、護膝等裝備，結合示威慣常狀況一併考慮，還有正常人會否管有不尋常兼威力相當驚人的弩，這樣又是否足夠推論。上訴方指若不考慮示威狀況，則未必足夠。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210107/AJ3ZG3GG3FAV7POWZ5AMZKATXU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210107%2FAJ3ZG3GG3FAV7POWZ5AMZKATXU%2F&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z6hYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=0c17ec44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210107%2FAJ3ZG3GG3FAV7POWZ5AMZKATXU%2F&h=cc8c3952\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210107/AJ3ZG3GG3FAV7POWZ5AMZKATXU/</a>"},{"pid":"0f842e29d11bffe11be6646ed1d7e6a06e01d5d4","tid":2357424,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:28:33.000Z","msg":"律政司認為純屬手民之誤。<br />\n<br />\n法庭都可以做差不多先生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d772d3df6b63e1075b33b060d6d84a15b67173","tid":2357424,"uid":126371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:30:22.000Z","msg":"鄭狗仆街死"},{"pid":"2152d1ecf4a2ac226516bb48f3b7bffaaf9ccac1","tid":2357424,"uid":156073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f038d26eba9764787ff573fe7a723de16e6648e","tid":2357424,"uid":288304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:33:03.000Z","msg":"法官大人，請問你有冇J？有？沒有？<br />\n<br />\n有的話姐係必然會用來強姦？"},{"pid":"e841fb04953a98acc1180593021fd0928e789586","tid":2357424,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b838ca6b1042799328c5af563c16407adc557c6","tid":2357424,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:13:30.000Z","msg":"咁尖啲箭，射出嚟唔少嘢喎<br />\n<br />\n唔係話射唔出 同有其他用途咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:36:29.000Z","msg":"佢唔接納其他用途,  但又冇其他助證屋企啲野係用黎示威用<br />\n有證人話佢中意整, 又整左好多年弩箭又唔信<br />\n辨方個舉例就係連登仔常用嘅屋企收埋菜刀嘅危險可當作武器嘅物品"},{"pid":"9cd3ebafa938a5e90a3ddea260407efe9007d043","tid":2357424,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:54:59.000Z","msg":"簡單黎講<br />\n1.辯方唔知鄭畜有自己考慮到成個港島示威環境黎判刑<br />\n原審討論係集中係手足在場附近情況(非衝突現場)同手足身上有咩物品<br />\n<br />\n2.鄭畜冇嚴格論證手足屋企物品係用黎意圖傷人, 只係因為佢第一條罪名入左所以第2條罪名就一齊入埋, 但兩條罪名冇連帶關係<br />\n<br />\n連帶關係例子:<br />\n因為你參加遊行個陣戴口罩, 而你被判非法集結罪名成立, 咁會中埋蒙面法"},{"pid":"9e18ba0ef2cfa4c4a9066666da28593adce61860","tid":2357424,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:05:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97fbd9546c54aac67736023b46d70553ea737d28","tid":2357424,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"9cd3ebafa938a5e90a3ddea260407efe9007d043","tid":2357424,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:54:59.000Z","msg":"簡單黎講<br />\n1.辯方唔知鄭畜有自己考慮到成個港島示威環境黎判刑<br />\n原審討論係集中係手足在場附近情況(非衝突現場)同手足身上有咩物品<br />\n<br />\n2.鄭畜冇嚴格論證手足屋企物品係用黎意圖傷人, 只係因為佢第一條罪名入左所以第2條罪名就一齊入埋, 但兩條罪名冇連帶關係<br />\n<br />\n連帶關係例子:<br />\n因為你參加遊行個陣戴口罩, 而你被判非法集結罪名成立, 咁會中埋蒙面法"}}